HEADWORD: Bushranger
<hw>Bush"ran`ger</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who roams,
or hides, among the bushes; especially, in Australia, an escaped
criminal living in the bush.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

